<AUTHOR>Justin</AUTHOR>
<TEXT>I have driven this car for 18 months. I have had no problems to date. It handles very well in snow, rain, and muddy dirt roads. Fuel economy is around 24-25, but decreases significantly with anything on the roof. I just installed two infant seats and barely fit them in. I am 5'10" and had to pull the seat 1 click forward from my usual position to fit them in. If you have long legs and plan on adding a car seat, buy different car. </TEXT>
<FAVORITE>Removable plastic deck in rear. 4WD. Low roof height for rack access. Fold flat seats </FAVORITE>
